window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Knox Whiteshaw is my husband.</b><br> <br> He’s also an egotistical psychopath who refuses to divorce me—even when I ask nicely.<br> <br> It doesn’t matter that I’m trying to move on with the goalie of his NHL team. Knox is dead set on ruining everything.<br> <br> My upcoming wedding, my future, my sanity…<br> <br> The man can hold a grudge like no other, and I am public enemy number one. I have been for six years, ever since he threatened me and stormed out of my life.<br> <br> Now that we’re forced back in each others’ lives, it’s only a matter of who will break first: him or me.</p>"; 
